Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Ike on Thursday night advised fellow housemate, Diane on her relationship life in the house. DAILY POST recalls that Diane sworn not to have any relationship with any male housemate in the ‘Pepper Dem’ edition.’ Diane, speaking with Esther and Mercy said she does not like or would date any male housemates because they are not her ‘Spec.’ According to her, she is not distracted by the new introduction of male housemates as they are all short and light-skinned men. However, a ‘romantic relationship’ seems to be stirring up between her and Elozonam as both housemates have been seen hanging out at every moment. Ike speaking to Diane on Thursday advised her to forget about ex-BBNaija housemate Tuoyo and date Elozonam. According to him,”Tuoyo is the least of them for you , if he comes here now, I will beat him up. “I like Elozonam and want you guys together. He is my cousin and fits you. “Stop thinking of Tuoyo, Elozonam needs you, he’s hot. Relax with your guy,”Ike tells Diane. DAILY POST recalls that evicted Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Nelson, after eviction said he stopped liking fellow housemate, Diane and moved on to Esther after Tuoyo told him he had interest in her. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.